model.mechanics
Interface Analytical

All Superinterfaces:
ModelContext
public interface Analytical
extends ModelContext

The analytical model. It consists of a strong formulation of a problem, {\em i.e.}, the governing differential equation to be imposed at every point of the domain and a set of pre-defined boundary and initial conditions. Then, one writes an equivalent weak formulation, {\em e.g.}, Galerking formulation.
